  "text": "Sensory analysis was carried out as described by [CITATION_1] . Each of the 8 trained panelists evaluated the samples of puree in duplicate in a total of 13 sessions. Sensory attributes (sweetness, fiber perception, and off-flavors) were measured on semi-structured visual scales labeled from 0 to 10. All tests were carried out in a room designed for sensory tests that fulfilled the standards set out by the International Organization for Standardization (ISO 8589, 2007) .",
